Mourinho on Sanchez, &quot;I don't know, it's not good for him, for the team or for me. There isn't anyone to blame. The club is making the effort and I have to respect the US authorities. Hopefully he can join us later.&quot;<br />
<br />
Mourinho, &quot;Dalot is injured but we knew that. We didn't want to lose him because of that. I think he'll be ready to start training when we go back to the UK. He'll be back in September.&quot;

